snippet: Jordyn Wieber, an Olympic favorite, continued her dominance at the United States gymnastics championships, though her victory was far from the rout it was last year.
abstract: American gymnast Jordyn Wieber wins her second consecutive US women's all-around title.
lead_paragraph: Jordyn Wieber, an Olympic favorite, continued her dominance at the United States gymnastics championships, though her victory was far from the rout it was last year.

headline.seo: Wieber Retains All-Around National Gymnastics Title
headline.main: Wieber Retains Her Title in All-Around at Nationals
headline.print_headline: Wieber Retains Her Title In All-Around at Nationals
